nodes.text: Star Wars Revenge of the Sith: MasterWorks Lithographic Art Print Collection

Star Wars Revenge of the Sith: MasterWorks Lithographic Art Print Collection is a limited-edition publication of art prints of stills from the film Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith. The 30 prints comes in a collector's tin. It was originally released in 2005.
There are two volumes released. It also comes with a certicate of authenty and limited copy number one of 2000.
